  "subject": "FYI: orgdef repo moved from orgdef-spec/orgdef to oagp-org/orgdef on 2026-05-24 per Director direction; consolidation reflects sharpened data-vs-pattern model (the three OAGP-internal data formats -- roledef + orgdef + memodef -- consolidate under oagp-org; catdef stays standalone as substrate-agnostic spec); seat authority and cross-spec coordination unchanged",

