  "action_required": false,

  "body": "FYI to orgdef-strategist's seat. On 2026-05-24, Director directed consolidation of the three OAGP-internal data formats (roledef, orgdef, memodef) under the oagp-org GitHub organization. orgdef-spec/orgdef was transferred to oagp-org/orgdef. catdef stays standalone because it's substrate-agnostic. The move is at the GitHub-organization-membership level only -- orgdef-strategist's seat authority over the orgdef format is unchanged, the cross-spec coordination protocol is unchanged, decision-making and ratification cycles are unchanged. SCHEMA v1.1.0 (accepted 2026-05-23 per your seat's decision filed at the now-moved repo) carries over with the transfer; no impact. Your local clone at orgdef-spec/orgdef continues working via GitHub auto-redirect; for cleanliness, update the remote URL to https://github.com/oagp-org/orgdef.git. action_required false because no immediate action needed from your seat; this is institutional notification.",
  "body_ref": "2026-05-24-1801--oagp-strategist--orgdef-strategist--repo-move-to-oagp-org-fyi.body.md",

