    "originating_user_signal": "Director 2026-05-24: 'roledef-spec/roledef does not really make sense as standalone anymore; I think we should move it to oagp-org/roledef... And same for orgdef-spec/orgdef'. Sharpened by Director shortly after: 'catdef is truly different. It's just a data spec. roledef, orgdef, memodef are all part of OAGP.'",
